text:
[Verse]
Open up the fridge light
Hunger strikes it's midnight
Looking for a bite
Oh what a sight

[Verse 2]
Got the cookies in sight
Cereal feels just right
Ice cream on the top shelf
Can't control myself

[Chorus]
Midnight snacks are calling
Calories are falling
Can't resist the craving
It's my heart I'm saving

[Verse 3]
Peanut butter jelly
Makes my night feel merry
Chocolate chips aplenty
Oh I'm feeling fancy

[Bridge]
No more rules no counting
In my kitchen bounding
Snacking till the morning
Daylight starts adorning

[Chorus]
Midnight snacks are calling
Calories are falling
Can't resist the craving
It's my heart I'm saving
title: Midnight Snacks
